{"tid":206831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被虐貓貓籌錢做手術 ，無良心中女善款都呃","createTime":"2017-04-18T14:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T15:58:47.000Z","uid":42044,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc15c493ffba3c47761c2f059437b8a86e1f9a9d","tid":206831,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:57:55.000Z","msg":"代post,主腳不是我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfb大量 wtsapp 圖做證據<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知呢度唔係關注流浪動物的平台<br />\n錢我也預左收唔返<br />\n純粹0係度俾大家 alert 下呢個呃善款的女人<br />\n<br />\n我係流浪貓狗拯救會的貓義工Emily，<br />\n是咁的&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n早前我地在斜坡救左一隻成條頸爛晒的被虐小貓布丁（總知就係有2個師奶掉左丁丁落斜坡，用條硬嘅膠頸帶cool到佢條頸爛晒，餓到見骨，詳情請睇協會page）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/pg/lovelycatcathome/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=1598205933530146&amp;ref=page_internal&amp;mt_nav=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fpg%2Flovelycatcathome%2Fphotos%2F%3Ftab%3Dalbum%26album_id%3D1598205933530146%26ref%3Dpage_internal%26mt_nav%3D1&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=18f21852\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/pg/lovelycatcathome/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=1598205933530146&amp;ref=page_internal&amp;mt_nav=1</a><br />\n<br />\n丁丁條頸血肉模糊，緊急做過兩次手術，住左個幾月已經用左超過HKD$20000， 醫生話因為傷口太大， 丁丁仲要住多2-3個月，每日住院費最少HKD$450。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/224733_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F224733_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=9d561cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地個會只有1-2個義工做暫託，真係能力十分之有限，幸好有善長們舉行義賣，而我亦都舉辦傳心班籌款及接傳心case，全數撥入丁丁嘅醫藥費。<br />\n<br />\n我冇諗過，有人竟然連捐款都可以呃！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/224918_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F224918_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d670b5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/224927_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F224927_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=36c65b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有個叫Pauline Cheung （Cheung Po Ling） 的人搵我同佢隻狗狗做傳心，當時已講明收費係俾丁丁的，$80 @一條問題。張小姐於是就問5條問題，呢度 HKD$400&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後佢又話想報讀動物傳心慈善班，學費HKD$850 @ 一位，Total HKD$1250。於是我就叫佢一次過入數，31/3之前要入&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n到31/3，梗係無入啦。之後佢話未出糧，好好聲氣問我傳心班可否照上，但上完過幾日先俾。我話ok，因我真心想佢同佢隻狗開心返。我見佢好眉好貌，信佢唔會連捐款都呃。<br />\n<br />\n點知堂又上埋，入數deadline 已過又冇聲氣，wtsapp問佢次次睇完msg都唔應機，於是我在傳心班嘅 Group度問，結果，即Quit Group！同時，更Del埋我Facebook&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n好啦佢玩潛水，我地就在協會出post 交代呢件事啦，都引起小小回響，佢見到我地個post, 就浦頭 wtsapp 返我話中傷佢之類，我有話唔俾錢咩，又話我唔del post 我係唔會俾，耍足我幾星期，結果，佢話佢朋友入左400蚊（仲要無入數紙，我日日咁多善長捐錢入黎我點證明呢400蚊係你入），下，仲有果850呢，佢話唔會俾，因為上完堂之後，傳唔到心。<br />\n<br />\n但佢上堂時，3次傳心都傳到！但返到屋企唔練習，就話傳唔到！其他學生都冇問題！<br />\n唔通返學讀書補習，考第尾，又可以唔比學費？？？仲要係捐款，我自己$1都冇袋落袋&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n如有人識佢，煩請叫佢還錢！<br />\n有人pm我地，話呢個Pauline Cheung 7年前已經係咁，次次都話未出糧，住黃大仙龍x樓，27歲<br />\n<br />\n詳情:<br />\n內有whatsapp對話cap<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://facebook.com/pg/lovelycatcathome/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=1648059928544746&amp;ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fpg%2Flovelycatcathome%2Fphotos%2F%3Ftab%3Dalbum%26album_id%3D1648059928544746%26ref%3Dpage_internal&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=8f0fa142\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/pg/lovelycatcathome/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=1648059928544746&amp;ref=page_internal</a>"},{"pid":"00464913a22680bb42e0d98099f7ee180f7c5ba1","tid":206831,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd7e7566c9eac774c282ca3166b8013ccd99ca1","tid":206831,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/paulinebb35?ref=page_internal&amp;__tn__=R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpaulinebb35%3Fref%3Dpage_internal%26__tn__%3DR&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=6f4957b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/paulinebb35?ref=page_internal&amp;__tn__=R</a>"},{"pid":"67ce8c41bfd64c206fb71d7a4df4095d62b04409","tid":206831,"uid":25354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻貓而家點"},{"pid":"043c68acd4b1496d0192c28d181797416d373003","tid":206831,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"真係呃嘅話，直接報警，喺度講係乜都做唔到"},{"pid":"fd8cacf4384f748e72e2bdcb8c6e01612f9f3899","tid":206831,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"汽車推推,等當事人回應"},{"pid":"6c670566a90eb672521f194ecf8ecd0a946dd5c4","tid":206831,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻貓而家點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傷口縮細中架喇，但仲係見倒血肉"},{"pid":"fcbbbc0e1c39f7ab3ba59094463bed88886ccd2e","tid":206831,"uid":24045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"咩叫傳心"},{"pid":"f0cbdae947fef41422ca61ff28d563a781cfb8ef","tid":206831,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫傳心</blockquote><br />\n同貓貓狗狗溝通"},{"pid":"aae0405852948dc339d9396b41a18b89ceb47def","tid":206831,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:38:16.00